### Backend API Testing - HTTP Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. API Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 3. Simple Search - Blue Dress
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "blue dress",
  "maxResults": 3
}

### 4. Search with Color Filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "shirt",
  "filters": {
    "color": "blue",
    "priceRange": [50, 100]
  },
  "maxResults": 5
}

### 5. Search with Budget Filter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "dress",
  "filters": {
    "priceRange": [100, 200]
  },
  "maxResults": 5
}

### 6. Search with Occasion Filter
